Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:06.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,几周之前 一个隐形的穹顶从天而降\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}A few weeks ago an invisible crashed dome crashed down
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.09,0:00:08.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,罩住了彻斯特磨坊镇 把我们和外部世界隔绝开来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}on Chester's Mill, cutting us off from the rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.43,0:00:11.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶是怎么来的 其中蕴含着什么奥秘\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Why the dome is here, what mysteries lie ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:12.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们还不知道\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}we still don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.77,0:00:15.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,每一天都试探着我们的底线\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Every day it tests our limits,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:18.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们内心深处的善与恶 一览无余\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}bringing out the best and the worst in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.73,0:00:23.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有人说我们会永远被困在这里面\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Some say we'll be stuck here forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.01,0:00:26.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是 我们决不放弃 坚持寻找逃出穹顶之法\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}but we will never stop fighting to find a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:28.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦 汉特 梅 这是我儿子戴尔\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Oh, Hunter May, meet my son Dale.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:29.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们需要你施展魔力\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}We need you to work your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:30.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,再发一条信息\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}to send one more message
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:31.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,到穹顶里面\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}into the dome
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:33.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-芭比 -别跳\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}- Barbie! - Don't jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:34.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,芭比\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Barbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:36.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许抓走芭比的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Maybe the guys who took Barbie
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:37.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就是那些觊觎蛋的人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}are the same ones who want the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:38.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们是怎么知道的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}How would they even know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:39.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们要保护好它\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}We'll protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:41.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,最安全的地方\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No better place to hide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:42.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就是躲到我爸的眼皮底下\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}than right under my dad's nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:44.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们都认为是它驱动着穹顶\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And you all think it powers the dome?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:46.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这就是它运行的机理 是吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}That's the-the working theory, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:47.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:48.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我的职责就是带领镇上的人们\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It's my job to lead the people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:51.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,重获自由\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}of this town to freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:54.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:56.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她是我的一个朋友 波林 佛多\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}She's a friend of mine... Pauline Verdreaux.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:00:58.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-波林 雷尼 -吉姆的母亲\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}- Pauline Rennie? - James' mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:01:00.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得那扇门是通往穹顶的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I think that door's the way back into the dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:02.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道它在哪儿 就出现在那里\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I know where this is. Grew up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.22,0:01:03.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好的 我们走 走\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}All right. Let's go, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:06.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,神马情况\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:08.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不知怎的我们回来了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}We're back somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:10.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,波林\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Pauline?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.19,0:01:15.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,波林\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Pauline?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:21.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:23.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这不可能 你\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}That's impossible. You...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:26.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你在这儿干什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:34.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是穹顶把你传过来的吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Did the dome send you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.48,0:01:36.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,像琳达和杜迪那样过来折磨我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Like Linda and Dodee to torment me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.92,0:01:38.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:40.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是的 吉姆\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:42.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是真正的我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It's really me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:44.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:46.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 你已经死了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No. You died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:48.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你九年前就已经死了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You died nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:50.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我一直没有死\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I was never dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:52.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你的车撞到了树上\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You drove your car into a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:56.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,残骸我都看到了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I... I saw the wreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:58.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我还看到了新闻报导\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I read the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:02.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还是我取出了你的骨灰\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I picked out your casket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:04.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我并不在那辆车里面\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I was never inside the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:06.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,车里面坐的是一具死尸\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It was a cadaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:09.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,莱斯特 科金斯 帮我伪造的 莱尔也帮了我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Lester Coggins helped me. And Lyle, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:10.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他知道用什么方法可以让整辆车烧起来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}He knew what to use to make the car burn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,烧得一无所剩\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}so that there would be nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:17.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-这是唯一的办法了 -什么唯一的办法\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}-It was the only way! -The only way for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:20.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是逃离彻斯特磨坊镇的唯一办法\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It was the only way to get out of Chester's Mill!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:25.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我跟你说过我的预感\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I told you about my visions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.93,0:02:27.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你也看过我画的画\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You saw my paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:29.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道肯定会发生可怕的事情\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I knew something terrible was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:32.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后你就自己逃走了 抛弃了我和朱尼尔\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}So you ran away and left me and Junior?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:35.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我这么做是为了保护我的家人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}To protect my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:37.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我以为穹顶是跟着我走的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I thought the dome would follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:39.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而且你绝对不会允许我离开\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And you would never let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:41.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你竟然还有脸站在这儿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You're gonna stand here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:46.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,站在你儿子的房间 在我面前找借口\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}in your son's room and make excuses to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:47.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,别说了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:49.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是你毁了他 波林\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You destroyed him, Pauline.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:54.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-你毁了你自己的儿子 -别再说了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}- You destroyed your own son. - Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:58.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这么多年了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}For all these years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:00.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我还以为是我的错\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I thought it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:02.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,吉姆\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Jim...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:04.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,吉姆\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Jim?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:06.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可是我又回来了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:10.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,吉姆 我回来呀\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Jim, I came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:16.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看看这个\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:18.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看到奇怪的东西了吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}See anything strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:21.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,叶子枯萎了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Its leaves have turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:23.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就好像秋天一样\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Like it's fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:25.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可是现在是夏天\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Except it's summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,过去两天气温骤降\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}The temperature's dropped in the last two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:29.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是棵橡树\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}This is an oak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:32.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是最先发生变化的树\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}One of the first to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:34.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得是什么情况\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Any idea why this is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:37.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不知为何 穹顶加速了季节变迁\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Somehow the dome is accelerating the seasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:41.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,往常 秋天是我的最爱\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Normally, fall's my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:44.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在火炉边上看书 再来杯加州葡萄酒 但是\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Book by the fire, nice glass of pinot, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这太奇怪了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}this is just odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:49.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,噢我的天\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:52.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Julia?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:54.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Julia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:04.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-你回来了 -是的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}- You came back. - I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:07.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我要带所有人出去\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'm gonna get everybody out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:09.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:11.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么会在这儿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}How are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:19.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,芭比 你特么怎么回来的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Barbie, how the hell did you get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:23.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们到屋里说吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Let's talk inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,外面冻死人了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:28.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这儿是什么时候变成阿拉斯加的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Since when did it become Alaska in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这还真不是个玩笑\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:34.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而且 嗯\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:36.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒妮不在\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Melanie's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔也不在\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Junior either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:40.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这个地方完全属于咱俩\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}We have the whole place to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:43.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们最好互相取个暖\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Better keep each other warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:51.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,等等 梅勒妮已经不在一天了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Wait. Melanie hasn't been here in, like, a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:54.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她可能在茱莉亚那儿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}She's probably at Julia's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:58.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,或是在外面做简方达健身操\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Or out doing Jane Fonda exercises,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:00.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,或是80年代土老帽做的那些事\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}whatever people did in the '80s.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:02.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗷 回来嘛\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Oh, come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦我的天 乔 蛋不见了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Oh, my God, Joe. The egg is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,啥\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:07.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得是她拿的吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You think she took it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:09.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,从她这么尽力保护这个蛋来看 我打赌是她拿的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}The way she protects that thing, I bet she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:12.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,走 我们去找她\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Come on, let's go find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:25.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Junior?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:29.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,噢 对不起\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Oh. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:31.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不是有意吓你的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I didn't mean to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:34.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没事儿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:37.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我该走了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:39.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚一定在担心了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Julia might be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:42.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不该让我们俩都睡着的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I shouldn't have let us fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:46.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果她因为我没回家而发火的话 我就把责任推到你身上\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}If she's mad I didn't come home, I'll just blame it on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我就跟她说是你把我锁在这了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Tell her you locked me up down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:50.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我开玩笑的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I-I was just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:00.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你确定蛋在这下面会安全吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}you're sure the egg's safe down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:05.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这个地方是为抵挡原子弹而建的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Uh, this place is built to withstand nuclear bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是镇上最安全的地方了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It's the safest place in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:08.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:11.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那我们一会儿见\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I guess I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:15.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好的 一会儿见\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Uh, yes. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:36.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Junior!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:39.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,安琪\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Angie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:41.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你想想你到底在做什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Think about what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是说和她在这下面\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}With her down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,事情不是你想的那样\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It-it's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:52.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是想跟着心走 还是免了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You're gonna want to follow your heart. Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:56.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不懂你在说什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I-I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:58.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Junior?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你刚说了啥\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:06.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:07.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,拜拜\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,拜拜\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:19.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,安琪\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Angie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,安琪\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Angie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:34.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:42.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以你跳下了一个地下的悬崖\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}So you jump off an underground cliff
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后莫名其妙地到了顶点镇\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and somehow land all the way in Zenith?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:46.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还在一个操场上醒来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Where you wake up on a playground.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:48.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我也觉得很惊讶\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It surprised the hell out of me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:50.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但同样的事也发生在山姆身上\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But the same thing happened to Sam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:51.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有莱尔\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:53.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那你还好吗 有没有身体上的受伤\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And you feel okay? No physical injuries
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,或者什么心理障碍\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}or-or psychological disturbances?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:57.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,到那的路很模糊 但\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}The way there was a blur, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:59.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但我醒过来了 我没事\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}but I woke up, I was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,回去的路\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}The way back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:05.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我很久之前就有这个记忆\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I had this memory from a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:07.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只是一些\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It was just something
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我小时候的回忆\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}from when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:13.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,其他人怎么样\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}How'd the others fare?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,莱尔\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Well, Lyle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:19.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他没有和我们一起从水里出来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}He didn't come up out of the water with the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他死了吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:21.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:22.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道的 也许他先上来了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You know, maybe he came up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:24.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许他溺死了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}He drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:26.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,又或者他陷在其中的某个地方\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Or maybe he's trapped somewhere in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:28.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道 最重要的是\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I don't know. What matters is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:29.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们能够利用那个悬崖\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}that we can use that cliff
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:31.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,把大家都带出去\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}to get everybody out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:32.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但我们需要一个计划\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But we need a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:34.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们最不想看到的就是混乱和惊逃\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Last thing we want is a stampede.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:36.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们先从我们信任的人开始\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Let's start with the people we trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:38.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我会找汤姆和安德里亚\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I will walkie Tom and Andrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让他们在一小时后在蔷薇酒吧见面\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Have them meet us at the Sweetbriar in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:43.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:46.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,终于有可以出去的路了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}There's finally a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:49.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道我们应不应该接受\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And I don't know if we should take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:54.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒妮\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Melanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:55.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,山姆\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:56.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么还活着\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}How are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:58.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我在那次掉落中活了下来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I survived the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:59.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,听我说 我不是要回去伤害任何人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Listen, I'm not back to hurt anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:01.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,尤其是你\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Especially you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:02.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你杀了我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You killed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:04.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那天晚上不是我推你进那个坑里\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I didn't push you into the crater that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以那就是莱尔咯\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}So, it was Lyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:09.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我帮忙埋葬了你\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I helped bury you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:12.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们都帮忙了 然后我们就跑走了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}We all did. And then we ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:15.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,从那天起我每天都在后悔\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And I've regretted it every day since.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:26.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,想象一下如果你相信我 保护好那个蛋\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Imagine if you'd trusted me, and protected the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许这些事都不会发生\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Maybe none of this would've happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:31.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许穹顶也不会降下来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Maybe the dome wouldn't have come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:33.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许也没有人会死\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Maybe no one would've died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:34.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒妮\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Melanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:39.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我真的很抱歉 梅勒妮\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I am so sorry... Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:40.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,为了所有的事\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}For everything..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:43.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我还有很多没完成的事\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I have a lot of unfinished business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:46.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得这可能是我唯一的机会\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And I figured this might be my only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:53.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你永远不知道你还会有多少机会\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You never know how many chances you're gonna get.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:06.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,吉姆 你在做什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Jim, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:08.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我只是在想\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I was just thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:11.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们的事\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}About us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:19.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想也许我能把朱尼尔找出来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I thought maybe I'd find Junior out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:22.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这就像我离开的那一天\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It's exactly as it was the day I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:28.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是我让你活着的方式\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It was my way of keeping you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:31.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我常常来这里\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I used to come out here and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:34.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,盯着这些 想要弄清楚\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}stare at these and try to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是什么让你那么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}what made you so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,疯狂\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,痛苦\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Tormented.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:44.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你去了哪里 波林\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Where were you, Pauline?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:48.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么进到穹顶里的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}How did you get inside the dome?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:52.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,通过芭比家在顶点镇一座房子的地下室门\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Through a cellar door on Barbie's family property in Zenith.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:54.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,芭比吗 你在顶点镇看到戴尔和芭芭拉吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Barbie? You saw Dale Barbara in Zenith?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:57.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想这就是命运吧 他和我一起回来的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Fate, I guess. He came back with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:59.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有山姆 我以前的一个学生\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And Sam. And a former student of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:02.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有莱尔\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:04.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只是莱尔没有活下来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Except Lyle didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:07.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,听到这个消息我感到很难过\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'm sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:12.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但为什么你会想要 来这里\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But why would you want... to come here?
