Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.88,0:28:45.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们真的要把蛋给那些外面的人吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Do we really have to give it to those people out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.36,0:28:47.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只要咱爸看到你还活着\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Once our dad sees you alive again,
