Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.36,0:29:31.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你动摇了吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Are you having second thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.83,0:29:33.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 还是想逃出去\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Not about leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.96,0:29:36.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.73,0:29:38.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那你犹豫什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.07,0:29:45.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们是因为穹顶才认识的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}We met because of the dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.64,0:29:48.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而且我们从来没有对彼此谈过\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And we never really talked about you and me
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.58,0:29:50.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,逃到外面的世界之后作何打算\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}out in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.38,0:29:52.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦哦\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.95,0:29:55.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.42,0:29:58.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.42,0:30:01.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我希望你能一直陪在我左右\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I want you in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.72,0:30:04.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,无论我们能否逃到顶点镇\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}whether we end up in Zenith
