Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.14,0:30:57.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你别管我 诺瑞\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Don't worry about me, Norrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.01,0:30:59.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,最重要的是保护好蛋\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}All that matters is protecting the egg.
