Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.42,0:31:10.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不介意加乔麦克里斯特一个\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I got no problem adding Joe McAlister to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.30,0:31:18.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.54,0:31:27.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,马上归西了你倒还算冷静\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Pretty calm for a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.18,0:31:29.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你会过来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I figured you'd stop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.04,0:31:33.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不希望我会是这种结局\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I hope it doesn't have to end this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.08,0:31:34.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,安琪倒是希望她的结局不是你\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Angie hoped it wouldn't end with you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.85,0:31:36.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在她头上砍了一斧子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}swinging an axe down on her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.48,0:31:38.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我以为那样会瓦解穹顶\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I thought it would bring the dome down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.49,0:31:40.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果能让时光倒流 我愿意付出一切\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I would do anything to take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.52,0:31:42.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你把她的手镯放到我的枕头下面 诱使我以为\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You put her bracelet under my bed so I'd think
