Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.36,0:31:48.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我当时不知所措了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I didn't know what else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.10,0:31:50.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不用担心了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.10,0:31:51.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,很快就了结了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It'll be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.70,0:31:55.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔 我无法让时光倒流\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Junior, I can't take back what I've done.
