Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.44,0:31:59.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你说的是\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.44,0:32:01.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,用子弹杀你 太便宜你了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Bullet's too quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.68,0:32:06.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我要让你生不如死\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}- You still have to suffer. -
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.01,0:32:07.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,站起来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.65,0:32:08.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,站起来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.22,0:32:13.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,打我啊 快反击啊\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Hit me. Fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.52,0:32:14.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,反击啊\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.72,0:32:16.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,快反击\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.79,0:32:18.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,反击啊\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}- Fight back! -
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.17,0:32:29.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你对安琪所做的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'm gonna do to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.17,0:32:31.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我也要让你尝尝滋味\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}what you did to Angie.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.60,0:32:34.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔 快停手\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Junior, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.35,0:32:49.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,信号呢\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Where is the signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.35,0:32:52.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.86,0:33:01.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,走着\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.97,0:33:05.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好的 我们走\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.80,0:33:08.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,穿过橱柜 去悬崖那儿 快\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Through the locker and to the cliffs. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.94,0:33:15.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你不能杀他\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You can't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.21,0:33:18.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你凭什么回来 还来维护他\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}How can you come back and protect him?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.45,0:33:20.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,留着山姆还有用\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Sam still has a part to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.75,0:33:22.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有我们的双手\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}So does each of the hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.62,0:33:25.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果他死了 穹顶里的每个人都会受连累\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}If he dies, everyone under the dome will suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.86,0:33:28.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我爱你 他却把你从我这儿夺走了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I loved you, and he took you away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.32,0:33:30.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你从来没爱过我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You never loved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.36,0:33:32.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你把我锁起来 想要囚禁我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You locked me up, wanting to keep me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.86,0:33:34.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那不是爱\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}That's not love.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.97,0:33:38.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那只是占有欲\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}That is possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.27,0:33:40.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你何苦要做这些傻事\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Why do something that can't be undone
