Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.41,0:33:46.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你不是真的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You're not real.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.01,0:33:49.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你只是穹顶和我玩的把戏\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You're just the dome playing tricks on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.15,0:33:51.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔 我在告诉你不要去做\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Junior, I'm telling you not to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.32,0:33:54.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看着我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.45,0:33:56.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看着我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Look at me.
