Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.77,0:34:56.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在你得扔了它\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Now, you throw it over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.08,0:34:57.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那剩下的我们呢\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What about the rest of us?
