Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.43,0:36:35.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,救救我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.93,0:36:36.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.02,0:36:55.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔 你的舅舅在哪\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Junior, where's your uncle?
