Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.30,0:37:51.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果我早点杀了你 她就会死\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}If I'd killed you earlier, she'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.50,0:37:52.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 如果我不能\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Yeah, well, she still might
