Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.64,0:38:25.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.11,0:38:30.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You okay?
